---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page title="About" description="Local computer repair technician in Limerick with 10+ years experience. One person, not a faceless company. Honest PC and laptop repairs at fair prices. No upselling, no jargon - just fixing computers.">

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About 061 Tech</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-content">

      <div class="about-intro">
        <p class="lead">I'm Adam. I've been working in IT for over 10 years - system administration, technical support, the works. Now I fix computers for people in Limerick.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Why I started this</h2>
      <p>Getting a computer repaired shouldn't mean driving across town, waiting in a queue, and hoping for the best. I wanted to offer something simpler: you tell me what's wrong, I send a courier to collect it, fix it, and send it back. You don't have to go anywhere.</p>

      <h2>How I work</h2>
      <p>I'm not here to sell you things you don't need. If your computer can be fixed cheaply, I'll tell you. If it's not worth fixing, I'll tell you that too. No upselling, no jargon, no surprises on the bill.</p>
      <p>Every repair is done properly - quality parts, thorough testing, honest communication throughout. I treat your computer like I'd want mine treated.</p>

      <h2>What I won't do</h2>
      <p>I believe in being upfront about limitations:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Apple/Mac repairs</strong> - I focus on Windows PCs and laptops. For Macs, you're better off with an Apple specialist.</li>
        <li><strong>Data recovery from encrypted drives</strong> - If your drive is encrypted and you've lost the key, there's nothing I or anyone else can do.</li>
        <li><strong>Repairs that aren't worth it</strong> - If a repair would cost more than the device is worth, I'll tell you honestly.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The name</h2>
      <p>061 is Limerick's area code. Simple, local, memorable. That's the idea.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What you can expect</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Honest assessments</h3>
          <p>I'll tell you what's actually wrong and what it'll cost. No inflating problems to charge more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Fair prices</h3>
          <p>Competitive rates, no hidden fees. The quote you approve is what you pay.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Plain English</h3>
          <p>No unnecessary jargon. I'll explain things in a way that makes sense.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Quality work</h3>
          <p>Proper repairs with quality parts. All work tested before return and covered by warranty.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container cta-section">
      <h2>Need something fixed?</h2>
      <p>Get in touch. I'll give you an honest assessment and quote.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/book" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book a Repair</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Contact Me</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Page>

<style>
  /* Page Header */
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Main Content */
  .about-content {
    max-width: 650px;
  }

  .about-intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-content ul {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* Values */
  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
